name: twinkle twinkle little sprite
description: Though common as sprites might be in the realm of fantastic creatures, we often forget about their exceptional abilities. One of the most curious thing about these magnificent beings is their ability to see the physical manifestation of magic sparkling in the air, the very air that surrounds us too. Thing is, it can be quite captivating, I mean, imagine all the sparkles we're missing out. At least this little buddy is enjoying them, so for the time being, let's leave him alone in his awe.
